Class EntityListFile

java.lang.Object
com.boomexs.shapeseditor.EntityListFile
public class EntityListFile extends Object
The EntityListFile class handles the loading and saving of EntityList objects from and to files. It provides methods for serializing and deserializing EntityList instances.
